- Admin auth: Hover mailbox session in mail iframe (no OTP) â€” see `ccvaa-dev-memory`
- Hover mail iframe: same-origin proxy at `/admin/mail`; cookie/redirect/CSRF quirks matter
- Preview: Deployment Protection bypass via `.env.local`; mail proxy needs reachability to Hover
- Board/Purposes: collapsible sections; shared expand icon patterns
- Design: brand-first; avoid generic AI aesthetics

